        },
        {
            "id": 127,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#4",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 128,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  喔，陳年往事罷了，我只是在本來就滿是間隙的可悲親情之間插入了一些小小的......楔子。",
                "name": "“沙卒”"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 129,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  你為什麼想要知道這個？",
                "name": "“沙卒”"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 130,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#2",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 131,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  ......我在找一條線索，拜你所賜，我不得不終止了在伊巴特地區的調查。",
                "name": "懾砂"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 132,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#2",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 133,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  哦......線索。",
                "name": "“沙卒”"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 134,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  也許這也可以成為你信任我的契機，說說看吧，但願我能幫得上忙。",
                "name": "“沙卒”"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 135,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#2",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 136,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  我在找一個人。一個哥倫比亞的軍工實驗負責人。",
                "name": "懾砂"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 137,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#2",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 138,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  你在調查哥倫比亞的公司，為什麼？",
                "name": "“沙卒”"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 139,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#5",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 140,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  ......因為我最尊敬的人死在了一場可笑的意外裡。",
                "name": "懾砂"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 141,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#5",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 142,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  如果那真的只是場意外？",
                "name": "“沙卒”"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 143,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "avg_npc_172_1",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#5",
                "focus": 2.0
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 144,
            "prop": "name",
            "attributes": {
                "content": "  那我也要......得知真相。何況這也不是那些人踩著我兄長的死往上升官的理由吧？",
                "name": "懾砂"
            }
        },
        {
            "id": 145,
            "prop": "Character",
            "attributes": {
                "name": "char_304_hvrain#3",
                "name2": "char_379_sesa_1#5",
                "focus": 1.0
            }
